
DECWAR — News
-------------

Welcome, Captain.

This is the operator news file.  Anything you write here is what players see
when they type 'NEWS' at the command prompt.  Edit at any time — the file is
re-read on every NEWS command, so there's no need to restart the server.

Source heritage: this file is the analog of the 1978 PDP-10 DECWAR.NWS file
served via the original WARMAC.MAC NEWS routine (lines 4629–4676).

Common uses:
  * Tournament announcements ("Tournament Saturday at 20:00 EST")
  * Server maintenance windows
  * Patch notes when you upgrade the port
  * Galaxy-wide flavor text and trash-talk

When this file is missing, the in-game NEWS command falls back to a built-in
"No news today, Captain." placeholder.  See MANUAL.md for the player-facing
view and PORT.md for the persistence model.
